{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*3>}3{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}The verse in {\highlight7 <IT>}Isaiah{\highlight7 <ITC>} (45:7) on which this blessing is based concludes with the words, “and 
