{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*19>}19{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}God {\highlight7 <IT>}saw{\highlight7 <ITC>} that mankind would one day worship the sun and therefore created the moon to 
