{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*20>}20{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <IT>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}Ofanim, chayos{\highlight7 <ITC>} and {\highlight7 <IT>}serafim{\highlight7 <ITC>} refer to various classes of angels.Ð{\highlight7 <IT>}Avudraham{\highlight7 <ITC>}{\highlight7 <QL>}\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*21>}21{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}God elevated Himself above everything He created during the six days of creation.{\highlight7 <QL>}\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*22>}22{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}This sentence is based on the verse: {\highlight7 @hh}{\highlight7 <HEB>}\rtlch \'e4' \'ee\'c8\'ec\'c8\'ea\'c0 \'e2\'c5\'e0\'e5\'cc\'fa \'ec\'c8\'e1\'c5\'f9\'d1{\highlight7 {\ltrch @ee}}{\highlight7 {\ltrch<}{\ltrch ENG}{\ltrch>}}\ltrch ÐAdonoy has begun His reign He has 
clothed Himself with majesty ({\highlight7 <IT>}Psalms{\highlight7 <ITC>} 93:1).{\highlight7 <QL>}\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*23>}23{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}When man is rested from his everyday tasks and freed from everyday problems, he is able 
to thank God for all His blessings.{\highlight7 <QL>}\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*24>}24{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}God causes light to appear in stages, gradually. This is an act of great compassion for if He 
