3. the call to assume the yoke of God’s commandments, 4. the warning against heretical 
concepts, 5. the warning against straying after sinful desires, and 6. the warning against 
idolatrous worship.Ð{\highlight7 <IT>}Maseches Berachos{\highlight7 <ITC>} 12b{\highlight7 <QL>}\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ6>}{\highlight7 <SUP2.5>}{\highlight7 <*76>}76{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <SZ9>}{\highlight7 <SUP0>}Rabbi Meir says: “the blue thread of the fringes resembles the sea, the sea reflects the 
